cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image animation and motion modeling using learned keypoints and local affine transformations. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a generator network to combine appearance and motion information. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses a self-supervised formulation to decouple appearance and motion information. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating video sequences and animation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with motion modeling and animation of objects in images.
